headline: MarketAxess Announces Trading Volume Statistics for December and Fourth Quarter 2024
summary: NEW YORK, January 06, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX), the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, today announced trading volume and preliminary variable transaction fees per million ("FPM") for December 2024 and the fourth quarter ended December 31, 2024.1
